<HEADER>
A5402 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-KIDS-TV-NYT     04-04 0031
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-KIDS-TV-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   KIDS-TV (Undated) will not move in tonight's New York Times News
Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y. Times News Service, Apr. 4.
</P>
</TEXT>
