<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-04-04 21:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5572 &Cx1f; taf-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BBN-METS-NYT &LR;      04-04 0600
