<P>
   DOWNLOAD-MUSIC (Undated) _ Music off the Internet poses a threat
to record companies.
</P>
<P>
   MATRIX-BROTHERSFILM (Hollywood) _ A look at the brothers behind
the week's big film, ``The Matrix''. By Bernard Weinraub.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; COMMENTARY (Moved in ``k'' category)  &LR;
</P>
<P>
   SAFIRE-COLUMN (Washington) _ William Safire on NATO's strategy
in Kosovo.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; SPORTS (Moved in ``s'' category) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   BBA-YANKS (Los Angeles) _ Yankees advance, focusing on Roger
Clemens. By Buster Olney.
</P>
